---
// GrowthTrap.astro - Problem framework section
---

<section class="py-16 lg:py-24 bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-50 to-white section-divider">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    
    <!-- Section Header -->
    <div class="text-center mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">
        The 'Growth Trap' is killing your momentum
      </h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        Most B2B teams are stuck between two expensive, time-consuming paths. 
        There's a better way.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Comparison Grid -->
    <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mb-8">
      
      <!-- Agency Route - Problem Card -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-6 shadow-sm border-2 border-gray-200 relative">
        <div class="absolute -top-3 left-6 bg-red-100 text-red-700 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-medium">
          The Slow Path
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-4 mb-4">
          The Agency Route
        </h3>
        <ul class="space-y-3">
          <li class="flex items-start text-gray-600">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-red-500 mr-2 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
